<p>Dear <%= @user_name %>,</p>

<p>This is a reminder that your submission to Dryad entitled, "<%= @resource.title %>" is still in "Private for peer review"
    status and has not entered our curation process.</p>

<p>If your related article has been accepted or if you are ready to initiate the curation process and proceed to publication, please follow these steps:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Login to <a href="https://datadryad.org">https://datadryad.org</a></li>
  <li>Click on “My datasets”</li>
  <li>Click “Update” on your dataset</li>
  <li>On the final page of the submission form (Review and submit page), deselect the checkbox for "Private for peer review"</li>
  <li>Click "Submit"</li>
</ol>

<p>If your related article is still in the peer review process, you may ignore this email.</p>

<p>If your related article has been rejected or you will not be proceeding with
    the submission of this dataset, kindly contact us at
    <a href="mailto:<%= @helpdesk_email %>"><%= @helpdesk_email %></a>
    and we will withdraw your submission.</p>

